{
  "stem": "13469.8",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I carried on studying and working in Birmingham.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm very proud to have picked up the Brummie dialect very soon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'd like to think that I don't have too much of a German accent anymore, because generally in Birmingham, everybody seems to have accepted me as a Brummie.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on that basis, I tend to think that I haven't been affected by the Holocaust at all, because I'm just the same as everybody else who worked at BSA Tools or who-- all the friends who did their engineering degree or the friends that I played table tennis with.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I played lots of table tennis at that time, also some football from [INAUDIBLE], et cetera.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got my engineering BSE degree with first class honors in 1954.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went on to do a master's degree in thermodynamics in 1955 at Birmingham University, the one year that I've actually studied at a university.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I-- I haven't been at schools and universities very often in my life kind of thing, so I very much appreciated the Birmingham University, to see what it was like as a student, as a real student, and all the opportunities.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I played lots of sports in that year apart from studying as well.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I left BSA and eventually transferred to Lucas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I worked at Lucas, and Girling in particular, on braking systems for 1958 until 1990, so that's 32 years, initially, on the design and performance of braking systems.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I traveled a lot to Italy a lot, to Fiat and all that, and later on to Japan and I taught-- helped to teach the Japanese vehicle manufacturers on how to make disk brakes Nowadays, they know it better than we do over here.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
